cds env

tree

├── app
├── db
├── eslint.config.mjs
├── package.json
├── README.md
└── srv

cds env ls roots


$ cds env ls roots

roots = [ 'db/', 'srv/', 'app/', 'schema', 'services' ]

means files in db, srv and schema folders and schema.cds , services.cds files are watched and service will get created.
